name: Ginny Weds Sunny
story: The film follows headstrong Ginny who meets Sunny for an arranged marriage, but turns him down, and then shows how Sunny teams up with Ginny's mother to win her love.

name: Brothers by Blood
story:
The Sound of Philadelphia
A tale of family, friendships and betrayal in the violent world of the Philadelphia mob.

name: Angrezi Medium
story: When his daughter decides to further her studies in London, a hardworking Rajasthani businessman does everything in power to make her dreams come true.

name: The Secrets We Keep
story: In post-WWII America, a woman, rebuilding her life in the suburbs with her husband, kidnaps her neighbor and seeks vengeance for the heinous war crimes she believes he committed against her.

name: A Babysitter's Guide to Monster Hunting
story: A babysitter embarks on a mission to save a child who's been abducted by monsters.

name: Operation Christmas Drop
story: Congressional aide Erica (Graham) forgoes family Christmas to travel at her boss's behest. At a beachside Air Force base, she clashes with Capt. Andrew Jantz (Ludwig), who knows her assignment is finding reasons to defund the facility.

name: Mrs. Serial Killer
story: When a doctor gets jailed for a string of shocking murders, his loyal wife sets out to commit a copycat crime to prove his innocence.

name: Street Dancer 3D
story: A coming-of-age story based on the lives of street dancers.

name: Mucho Mucho Amor: The Legend of Walter Mercado
story: Every day for decades, Walter Mercado — the iconic, gender non-conforming astrologer — mesmerized 120 million Latino viewers with his extravagance and positivity.

name: Psycho Goreman
story: After unearthing a gem that controls an evil monster looking to destroy the Universe, a young girl and her brother use it to make him do their bidding.

name: Baby Done
story: Wannabe-adventurer Zoe freaks out when she falls pregnant to her long-term boyfriend Tim. As Tim embraces the prospect of fatherhood, Zoe attempts to rush through her dreams.

name: The 100 Candles Game
story:
El juego de las 100 velas   •   لعبة الشموع المائة
يجتمع مجموعة من الأصدقاء من أجل أداء طقوس لعبة غريبة، حيث تنص قواعد اللعبة على قص حكاية من حكايات الرعب في كل مرة، وسرعان ما تتحول ليلتهم لشيء أكثر دموية.

name: Torbaaz
story: A man rises from personal tragedy to lead a group of children from a refugee camp to victory, transforming their lives through the game of cricket.

name: Double World
story:
Zheng tu
Seeing the neighboring country become more and more powerful, a warlord organizes a competition to reveal the best warriors. A young man is eager to bring honour to his clan.

name: Freaks: You're One of Us
story: Tipped by a mysterious tramp, a meek fry cook discovers she has superpowers -- and uncovers an unsavory, vast conspiracy.

name: Phineas and Ferb the Movie: Candace Against the Universe
story: The famed stepbrother inventors know what they're gonna do today. They're gonna rescue their sister from an alien abduction.

name: Andhaghaaram
story: Supernatural events occurring in the lives of three people cluster to reveal a connection between the trio.

name: Boys State
story: A thousand 17-year-old boys from Texas join together to build a representative government from the ground up.

name: Baaghi 3
story: A man embarks on a bloody rampage to save his kidnapped brother.

name: The Forty-Year-Old Version
story: Radha is a down-on-her-luck NY playwright, who is desperate for a breakthrough before 40. Reinventing herself as rapper RadhaMUSPrime, she vacillates between the worlds of Hip Hop and theater in order to find her true voice.

name: Wotakoi: Love Is Hard for Otaku
story:
Wotaku ni koi wa muzukashii
Two office workers, who are also fans of otaku culture, meet and develop a relationship.

name: All Day and a Night
story: A young man who committed a homicide deals with the repercussions of his action.

name: American Wisper
story: In June 2016, a loving family was found shot to death at their suburban home in Northern New Jersey, and discovered by father and husband Josiah Wisper - a brash businessman who owned bars, restaurants and real estate in Harlem, New York.

name: Nocturne
story: An incredibly gifted pianist makes a Faustian bargain to overtake her older sister at a prestigious institution for classical musicians.

name: Bad Tales
story:
Favolacce
A few families living out on a limb in the suburbs of Rome. Tensions here can explode at any time; ultimately it's the children who bring about the collapse.

name: Unpregnant
story: A 17-year old Missouri teen named Veronica discovers she has gotten pregnant, a development that threatens to end her dreams of matriculating at an Ivy League college, and the career that will follow.

name: Class of '83
story:
Class of 83
The story of an upright policeman-turned-trainer whose wards deal with various complexities.

name: Chemical Hearts
story: A high school transfer student finds a new passion when she begins to work on the school's newspaper.

name: Jawaani Jaaneman
story: A 40 year-old playboy's life turns upside down when he comes to know that he has a 20 something year-old daughter.

name: Dick Johnson Is Dead
story: A daughter helps her father prepare for the end of his life.

name: Kiss the Ground
story: A revolutionary group of activists, scientists, farmers, and politicians band together in a global movement of "Regenerative Agriculture" that could balance our climate, replenish our vast water supplies, and feed the world

name: The Princess Switch: Switched Again
story: When Duchess Margaret unexpectedly inherits the throne to Montenaro and hits a rough patch with Kevin, it's up to her double Stacy to save the day before a new lookalike, party girl Fiona foils their plans.

name: Blackpink: Light Up the Sky
story: Chart the meteoric rise of the South Korean girl group BLACKPINK in director Caroline Suh's documentary.

name: Beastie Boys Story
story: Mike Diamond and Adam Horovitz of Beastie Boys tell you an intimate, personal story of their band, and their 40 years of friendship together.

name: Black Is King
story: Visual album from Beyoncé inspired by 'The Lion King'.

name: Skydog
story: Colt Lifestone, a high school senior working on his pilot's license, must rescue his mother with the help of stray dog called Oreo and his new friend Alice

name: Lootcase
story: Nandan Kumar comes across a suitcase and discovers it is full of cash. He takes the suitcase and soon finds himself being chased by a notorious gangster, an honest cop and a minister, who want the suitcase at any cost.

name: Holidate
story: Fed up with being single on holidays, two strangers agree to be each other's platonic plus-ones all year long, only to catch real feelings along the way.

name: American Murder: The Family Next Door
story:
جريمة قتل أمريكية: عائلة في المنزل المجاور
In 2018, 34-year-old Shanann Watts and her two young daughters disappear in Colorado. With the heartbreaking details emerging, the family's story made headlines around the world.

name: Over the Moon
story:
فوق القمر
يتناول العمل قصة طفلة تقوم بتصنيع وبناء صاروخ فضائي، من أجل السفر به عبر الفضاء في رحلتها إلى القمر على أمل مقابلة إلهة القمر، لتبدأ في خلال سعيها لتحقيق حلمها بسلسلة متلاحقة من التحديات.

name: The Christmas Chronicles: Part Two
story: Kate Pierce, now a cynical teen, is unexpectedly reunited with Santa Claus when a mysterious troublemaker threatens to cancel Christmas - forever.

name: Raat Akeli Hai
story: The film follows a small town cop who is summoned to investigate the death of a politician which gets complicated by the victim's secretive family and his own conflicted heart.

name: Reaptown
story: Carrie is freed from prison under the conditions of a work-release program in Reaptown. As she struggles to find her missing sister while working the night shift as a security guard, Carrie soon finds herself in the presence of evil.

name: Sadak 2
story: The film picks up where Sadak left off, revolving around the journey with a young girl who becomes an important character in the life of the protagonist, and the reason for him to stay alive.
